{"tid":2337561,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩男事隔半年被控違「限聚令」 一男因「私了」六旬婦案被定罪而不獲保釋","createTime":"2020-12-23T11:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T12:17:11.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e00decc08e9dc69ecbfaac73b3785add45cc5f36","tid":2337561,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:10:18.000Z","msg":"今年 5 月 10 日旺角爆發警民衝突，逾百人被捕，警方事隔半年後始控告兩名青年違反「限聚令」，原訂今午（23日）在九龍城裁判法院答辯，惟辯方要求進一步索取文件，故押後至明年 2 月 17 日獲批准。其中，22 歲青年另因「私了」老婦被判囚 8 個月，故本案押後期間不得保釋。<br />\n<br />\n兩被告原獲法庭批出擔保，惟方**因在同月6日天水圍的「和你唱」活動中，「私了」一名六旬婦人，被判囚 8 個月，故其在本案的擔保被撤銷"},{"pid":"3cfe38a10fe1e0895f25effdcf9fc46f05413716","tid":2337561,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:10:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/5-10-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92-%E5%85%A9%E7%94%B7%E4%BA%8B%E9%9A%94%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E9%81%95-%E9%99%90%E8%81%9A%E4%BB%A4-22%E6%AD%B2%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87-%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%86-%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E5%A9%A6%E8%A2%AB%E5%9B%9A%E4%B8%8D%E7%8D%B2%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F5-10-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%2594%25B7%25E4%25BA%258B%25E9%259A%2594%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%2581%2595-%25E9%2599%2590%25E8%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%25A4-22%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587-%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%2586-%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%2597%25AC%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%259B%259A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%258D%25B2%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%2F&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp2o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=da81af6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F5-10-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%2594%25B7%25E4%25BA%258B%25E9%259A%2594%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%2581%2595-%25E9%2599%2590%